translations</font></h1>
          <h1 align="center"
        style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font size="3"><font color="#FFFCBB" face="Times New Roman">An
        approach to the original singing of the Homeric epics and
        early Greek epic and lyrical poetry by</font> <font color="#FFFFFF" face="Times New Roman">Ioannidis
        Nikolaos</font></font></h1>
          <h1 align="center"
        style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><font color="#A3A3A3"><span style="font-weight: 400"><i><font size="3" face="Times New Roman"><strong style="font-weight: 400">
